--------------------------

-- All eZ publish versions from 3.5 and higher are now supported.

-- Fixed bug: Context menu didn't work in a table cell (IE).

-- Fixed bug: 'Insert' dialogs were displayed instead of 'Properties' (Mozilla).

-- Fixed bug: Link's attributes 'id' and 'title' were not stored.

-- Fixed bug: Window elements "blinking" (IE).

-- Fixed bug: Unable to insert custom tag into a table cell (Mozilla).

